title: Fingerprint Fee Was Received
body: On June 19, 2021, we accepted the fingerprint fee for your Form I-601A, Application for Provisional Unlawful Presence Waiver, Receipt Number YSC2190185001. Our Potomac Service Center location is working on your case. We mailed you a notice describing how we will process your case. Please follow the instructions in the notice. If you move, go to www.uscis.gov/addresschange to give us your new mailing address.

title: Case Was Received
body: On June 16, 2021, we received your Form I-751, Petition to Remove Conditions on Residence, Receipt Number YSC2190185003, and sent you the receipt notice that describes how we will process your case. Please follow the instructions in the notice. If you have any questions, contact the USCIS Contact Center at www.uscis.gov/contactcenter. If you move, go to www.uscis.gov/addresschange to give us your new mailing address.
